===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}
# [[extraordinary|Extraordinarily]] [[capable]] or [[knowledgeable]].
#: ''I am '''expert''' at making a simple situation complex.''
#: ''My cousin is an '''expert''' pianist.''
# Characteristic of an expert.
#: ''This problem requires '''expert''' knowledge.''

