===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A person with [[extensive]] [[knowledge]] or [[ability]] in a given subject.
#: ''We called in several '''experts''' on the subject, but they couldn't reach an agreement.''
# {{chess}} A player [[ranking]] just below [[master]].

